kpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Tam-Qu%E1%BB%91c-di%E1%BB%85n-ngh%C4%A9a-thi%C3%AAn-m%E1%BA%A1t-thi/poem-QWbvtZJBuf1WxDlFnPFXbw">Tam Quốc diễn nghĩa thiên mạt thi - 三國演義篇末詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-%E1%BB%B6/Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ti%E1%BA%BFn-t%E1%BB%ADu/poem-0fN-0XLrST_Hh-6xchdl-Q">Thương tiến tửu - 將進酒</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-%E1%BB%B6/author-AwmtxAvU68PUawMGR0lmaw">Ngô Ỷ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%ADch-du-T%C3%ADch-y%E1%BA%BFt-Hoa-C%C3%A1i-qu%C3%A2n/poem-crS01jzBUNbs6SoUtWJhPg">Tích du (Tích yết Hoa Cái quân) - 昔遊（昔謁華蓋君）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-h%C3%AD-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-N%C3%A3o-H%C3%A1c-s%E1%BB%A9-qu%C3%A2n-huynh/poem-u159qYrMs2x5zxJ5w9coLw">Xuân nhật hí đề Não Hác sứ quân huynh - 春日戲題惱郝使君兄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
